{"word":"G818 - ἀτιμάζω - atimázō - at-im-ad'-zo - Despise","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀτιμάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>atimázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>at-im-ad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Despise"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அவமானப்படுத்து, கனவீனம்பண்ணு, அவமானமடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to dishonor, insult, treat with contumely"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G820 - ἄτιμος - átimos - at'-ee-mos/820\">G820</a>; to <i>render infamous</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>contemn</i> or <i>maltreat:</i> - despise, dishonour, suffer shame, entreat shamefully."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}